ura]]'' || eastern mud snake || Colubridae || No || Low\n|-\n| [[File:Western Mud Snake.jpg|180px]] || ''[[Farancia abacura|Farancia abacura reinwardtii]]'' || western mud snake || Colubridae || No || Low\n|-\n| [[File:Rainbow Snake taken in Southern Georgia in June 2003 2.jpg|180px]] || ''[[Farancia erytrogramma|Farancia erytrogramma erytrogramma]]'' || rainbow snake || Colubridae || No || Highest\n|-\n| [[File:Heterodon platirhinos2.jpg|180px]] || ''[[Heterodon platirhinos]]'' || eastern hognose snake || Colubridae || No || Moderate\n|-\n| [[File:H Simus.jpg|180px]] || ''[[Heterodon simus]]'' || southern hognose snake || Colubridae || No || Highest,<br>Possibly extirpated\n|-\n| [[File:Lampropeltis calligaster calligaster.jpg|180px]] || ''[[Lampropeltis calligaster|Lampropeltis calligaster calligaster]]'' || prairie kingsnake || Colubridae || No || High\n|-\n| [[File:Lampropeltis calligaster rhombomaculata.jpg|180px]] || ''[[Lampropeltis calligaster rhombomaculata]]'' || mole kingsnake || Colubridae || No || Moderate\n|-\n| [[File:G-Bartolotti juv SK.jpg|180px]] || ''[[Lampropeltis elapsoides]]'' || scarlet kingsnake || Colubridae || No || Low\n|-\n| [[File:Lampropeltis getula getula.jpg|180px]] || ''[[Lampropeltis getula|Lampropeltis getula getula]]'' || eastern kingsnake || Colubridae || No || High\n|-\n| [[File:Speckled King Snake.jpg|180px]] || ''[[Lampropeltis getula holbrooki]]'' || speckled kingsnake || Colubridae || No || High\n|-\n| [[File:Black Kingsnake (Lampropeltis getula niger).jpg|180px]] || ''[[Lampropeltis nigra]]'' || black kingsnake || Colubridae || No || Low\n|-\n| [[File:Tennessee milksnake.jpg|180px]] || ''[[Lampropeltis triangulum triangulum]]'' || eastern milk snake || Colubridae || No || Moderate\n|-\n| [[File:Red milk snake.JPG|180px]] || ''[[Lampropeltis triangulum syspila]]'' || red milk snake || Colubridae || No || Moderate\n|-\n| [[File:Masticophis flagellum flagellum.jpg|180px]] || ''[[Masticophis flagellum flagellum]]'' || eastern c